https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=31453	30000
iFixit<a href="http://www.ifixit.com/teardown/Kindle-Fire-HD-Teardown/10457/1">分解了</a>亚马逊最新的7英寸平板Kindle Fire HD，给出了可修理得分7/10，认为这款平板对DIY用户比较友好。<i>
